# 8) Identify the stacking-fault ribbon between the partials (CNA code 2 =
#    hcp coordination) and measure its extent in the glide plane.  Note the
# screw can dissociate on either of the two {111} planes that contain its
#    line; the in-plane extent below is measured plane-agnostically.
compute cna all cna/atom 3.45
run 0 post no
